[Auction "S"]
1NT pass 2C pass 2D pass 3S pass 4S pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{Because NORTH holds a 4-card Major suit, (

♥

s), he starts his

responses with Stayman.

SOUTH denies holding any 4-card Major suit so NORTH gives up on

♥

s.

He next bids ♠s, showing five of them. He jumps to 3♠, giving SOUTH the choice

between 4♠ or 3NT.

With three trumps SOUTH chooses 4♠.}
