[Auction "E"]
1NT pass 2C pass 2D pass 2H pass 4H pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{WEST, with a 5-card AND a 4-card Major first uses Stayman.

EAST denies a 4-card Major, so WEST realizes that ♠s are out.

He then bids

♥

s, promising five of them.

EAST not only has three

♥

s, she also has 17 points so

she bids 4

♥

.}
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 4, chOption: W, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:3, nBasis: 0, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]

